Dialogs.Dialog: Hmm, addition theorem... and then... Okay, I've solved it！
Rinko
Good job, ▲主人公＊▲.
When did you arrive ▲小早川＊▲？
A little while ago.
...Sorry, I didn't notice.
I saw something good, so I don't mind.
Something good...？
The profile of a boyfriend who is trying his best.
Your hardworking profile looks so cool.
(I'm glad I'm doing my best！)
Rinko
Aren't you irresistible to girls these days, ▲主人公＊▲？
That was sudden.
"Kyaa, it's so cool he can solve such a hard problem！ So cool！" Don't they say that？
I don't get told that.
I see. Only Rinko thinks it's cool.
Huh...？
I-It's nothing.
Did you just say cool...？
I never said that！ ...You're an idiot.
Rinko
You are very popular, Sensei.
Sensei...？
You were teaching the other students. I watched you the whole time. You really looked like a sensei.
Haha... I just helped them because they said they didn't understand something in math class.
And you told them you would teach them. That's awesome.
Hey. Sensei. Will you teach Rinko math gently next time？▼
(Being a sensei... doesn't feel bad.)
(My experiment was a success... I feel good.)
Rinko
What are you doing, ▲主人公＊▲...？
Ah, nothing much. I'm just cleaning up an experiment, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hmmm... why are you on your own？
Well, I was in a good mood, so I just began cleaning.
Really, you're an... Well, never mind. I'll help you.
Eh, you don't have to.
It's okay. You're the only one whose experiment worked.
What, you knew！？
I know. You did your best.
(I'll work harder！)
(Perfect score on my physics pop quiz！ I worked so hard.)
Rinko
Um, you're not forcing yourself... right？
I didn't. What's wrong？
When I see my boyfriend trying too hard, I worry about him as a girlfriend.
If you fall down or something, even Rinko will be out of control.
Hey, hey. It's okay. I'm not pushing it.
...I see. That's good. I'll tell you what...
Huh？
I'm happy for you. That makes Rinko kinda happy... Congrats▼
(Glad I tried！)
(Perfect score on the quiz！)
Rinko
You know, you should teach Rinko math sometime.
Okay, but there's no easy strategy.
Is that so...？ Bummer. I thought Rinko was going to be good at science and math.
...Now, you must have thought that Rinko would never be able to do that.
No, I didn't！
It's in your expression. As a punishment, teach me to study gently and carefully.
You can't refuse, okay？ It's a punishment. It's one-on-one！
(I'd welcome this kind of punishment！)
Yay！ The teacher praised me. I worked hard on the grammar of the old Japanese texts.
Rinko
You're so excited just because you got a good grade. You're just a kid.
Even Rinko can afford that many problems, you know.
...Yeah, well, I'm glad it went nice.
You don't have to be so depressed. I said too much. I'm sorry.
Congratulations.
Huh？
Earlier, you see... there was someone looking this way. Once again... you did a great job. Congrats.
...But stop grinning.
(In your typical way, I'm getting motivated again, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Rinko
You know, ▲主人公＊▲...
That was a cool recital you did earlier.
Haha, I was so upset when he pointed at me out of the blue.
Without practice？ Just reading out loud...？
That sensei, he always does that.
Hey. Next time, you should teach reading tips to Rinko.
Tips, huh... I wonder if it's with emotion. Do you want to begin it here？
Here？ With emotion, huh... We can try, though.
I... really... love you... How's that, ▲主人公＊▲？
Yeah, I think that's good. (Was that my reward？)
(The evaluation of my essay was pretty good.)
Rinko
From the look on your face, it looks like your essay went well.
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲.
You should be pleased！？ I know. Your girlfriend will praise you.
What！？
That's great. It's perfect. I'm so happy. Rinko is so happy！
This feels quite fake...
Um... don't you get it！ How dull can you be？
In her own way, Rinko is doing her best to praise you...
(I'm glad to hear that！)
I finally got around to reading the book that was on my agenda！
Rinko
Oh... that's the book Rinko gave up on. I see... Nicely done.
When the teacher first gave me the assignment, I really thought it was impossible.
I think Rinko will give it another try...
That's right. Let's discuss our impressions once we've read it. Yup！
...Yeah. That sounds kind of fun.
Isn't it？
It's nice that we can inspire each other like this. I've been longing for it for a while... Hehe.
With you, I think Rinko can do her best in anything. Thank you.
(It took a lot of work, but it was worth the effort to get through it！)
I'm starting to feel like I'm as good as anyone in humanities！
Rinko
No one can beat you in humanities, huh. Not even Rinko. Hmmm.
Are you angry, ▲小早川＊▲...？
There's nothing wrong with having confidence.
(She's definitely mad... I think I got a little carried away.)
Hehe... surprised？ My boyfriend did his best. I can't be mad at him.
Wha-What...
Because, you know...
I like your hard-working nature very much... Good luck next time▼
(I feel like I could do better！)
Rinko
You did it, ▲主人公＊▲.
Eh... what do you mean？
There you go again. I meant the class you just had.
Your teacher praised you, didn't he？ He said, "Your interpretation of modern words in ancient Japanese is perfect."
That was quick！ How did you know that？
Hehe. My network of information on my boyfriend is perfect.
Your information network about me, huh...
I want to be the first to praise you. You know, as a girlfriend.
Nicely done... Hehe▼
(I will do my best next time too！)
I can't believe I'm saying this myself, but I think this picture might be my best work.
Rinko
...Hah.
Huh...？ You sighed, does that mean my picture is weird...？
I'm impressed. Looking at this color scheme, isn't it influenced by Fauvism？
Fu-Fauvism...？
I am sure that in the future you will be a gem of a person whose name will be engraved in the history of art.
Oh, that's right. I'll get your autograph.
You're overreacting！
Hehe... I guess. But Rinko really likes this picture.
(I'm most pleased with that assessment！)
I think I can say that I am quite confident in this picture.
Rinko
You were good at painting, ▲主人公＊▲...？
Not that much... I just like to draw.
Heh... let me see it.
Oh, maybe you're embarrassed？ Heh, well, let's take a closer look.
Y-You don't have to get so close... So, what do you think？
I'm not an expert, so I don't know if it's good or not, okay？
But Rinko loves the brush strokes, the coloring... everything. Rinko loves this painting. What more do you need？
(I did it！)
At this point, we are very close to completion.
Rinko
Can you show it to Rinko, ▲主人公＊▲...？
It's not finished yet, but... Do you want to see it？
I want to see. Heh... you have good taste. You draw pictures like this too？
I'm looking forward to seeing this one completed. Of course you'll show it to Rinko first, right？
Of course.
Yay. The perks of being a girlfriend, huh？ Hehe.
(She's looking forward to it, and I'm a few steps before finishing it！)
Rinko
You were surrounded by your classmates, ▲主人公＊▲？
I drew illustrations during art class, and a lot of people wanted them.
Show it to Rinko.
...It's soooo cool. It looks like it could be a character from a fighting game. If there were, I'd definitely use it！
I'm glad to hear you say that, because I drew it in your image, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko's image...？ Hehe, thanks. Can I have this illustration？ I'll take good care of it！
Oh... I'll redraw it better then！
This is fine. It's the one and only illustration in the world drawn for Rinko. That's enough.
(Glad you're happy with it.)
When a teacher praises you, it makes you more motivated.
Rinko
Hmm... Better than being complimented by Rinko？
Ah... no... did you hear that？
Your arts sensei has a good eye, too. Well, Rinko saw your talent a long time ago.
Eh, I see.
It's obvious. Do I have to tell you every time？
That is... well...
Then...
Rinko knows all your good points... Because I'm your girlfriend.
(I'm even more motivated if you tell me that ▲小早川＊▲！)
The chorus is bringing the class together！
Rinko
You were taking a firm leadership role, ▲主人公＊▲.
You're exaggerating.
In Rinko's class, no one can take the leadership...
What about you ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko as a leader？ Absolutely not！ I'm not that type of person.
I'd like to see it, though. The kind of leader you want to be, I think you can do it, ▲小早川＊▲.
Yo-You think so？
I'm sure... you're doing your best. Yes, I'll try my best too.
(Okay, I'll do my best！)
(Well played this time！)
Rinko
Music class, is it the same for men and women？
Yeah, I think so, but why？
I was just thinking about the other girls watching you play...
You know, you don't have to play so cool either.
You can play cool just in front of Rinko, that's all...
(Maybe you're jealous...？)
Today's class chorus was nice.
Rinko
I knew it was your class.
Ah, did you hear that, ▲小早川＊▲？
I just had to. I heard it. Well... I'm glad for you. It was good, but...
But...？
All I can hear is your voice.
Was I that loud？
Not really. It's kind of like...
It seems all Rinko can hear is her boyfriend's voice... Hehe.
I've been having a lot of fun playing these lately.
Rinko
You're doing great. You're looking good！
Do you think so...？
What？ You don't trust what Rinko says？
No, no, that's not true...
It's true. Your performance has a good sense.
(My good sense, huh... Alright, I'll do my best！)
(Well, it worked out this time！)
Ah, did you hear the performance this time, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Yeah. It was good, right？
Is that all...？
I'll leave it at that...
Geez... I can't help it.
It's cool and I'm kinda falling in love with you all over again... hehe▼
(Let's try harder next time！)
Yay. I beat my time！
Rinko
That's great. Practice makes perfect？
Am I too happy just to break my own record？
That's not true. That's a great record.
Do you think so？ I feel more confident when you say so, ▲小早川＊▲.
Well, then...
Hooray, hooray, go for it, go for it ▲主人公＊▲♪
...Hehe. Rinko is always rooting for you▼
(Yay！ I'll give it my best next time.)
Rinko
First place was a big achievement.
I guess！ I was feeling good today.
Hah... Why wasn't Rinko born another year earlier？
Huh？
Then, you know, I could be in the same class with you and cheer you on proudly.
You could have cheered me on.
That's... embarrassing. Everyone is watching. That's why...
Just make sure to show Rinko how much cooler you are...
(I'll do my best next time！)
Goal！ It feels good to score a final goal after all.
Rinko
I was so excited.
I want to show my good side in front of you, ▲小早川＊▲.
In front of Rinko...？
Of course！
You're so loud... Other people can hear you.
But, you know... I do think you're cool.
Huh？ I didn't hear you.
I said you're cool！ Geez... don't make me say it again. I'm looking forward to the next time.
(All right！)
Alright, we've got a comeback win！
Rinko
A last three-point shot！ I didn't think it would go in from that distance, did you？
Haha, I left it half to luck, though.
Luck is also a part of your ability. Right？
The goddess of fortunes has been watching over me！
You mean Rinko...？ Geez... you're embarrassing me！ Don't day it out loud.
It can't be helped. I'll allow it.
Huh？ I didn't hear you.
I said I'm going to be your goddess！ Don't make me say it again.
(Okay, I'll do my best！)
Hah... Hah, Hah... Okay, I finished the race！
Rinko
Good work. Long distance running for the boys？ That's tough.
If you dash... all the way... at the last minute, you can... Hah... Hah...
You're so serious about PE class... You're an idiot.
Haha, if I see you, I just want to give my all, ▲小早川＊▲.
For Rinko...？
I mean, it's a natural to do it in front of you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Then... I have to reward my boyfriend for such hard work, don't I？
It was really cool to see you doing your best▼
(Yay！)
It looks like there won't be much lending today. The only thing left to do is rearrange the bookshelves.
You don't have to run, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
It's because... Rinko's... on duty today, right？ Sorry.
Don't worry about it. I didn't have much work today.
...Yeah.
Don't be so downhearted. It's just that I took the turn on my own.
Well, next time it's your turn, Rinko will help you. Is that okay...？
Sure. Well, then, please.
Yes！ Oh... and... thank you for always helping Rinko▼
(Yay！)
Okay... The teacher's stamp on the list of supplies to be purchased concludes today's business！
Rinko
Supplies...... Oh, did I mention that they are running out of printer paper and such？
Oops, thanks. I'll add it to the list.
...Yay！
I've been relying on you a lot lately. I'm glad I was able to be of some help... hehe. It's strange, isn't it？
That's mutual.
I see. So it's mutual. Rinko is helping you too... I'm relieved.
Mutual... I like it, sounds good.
Yes！
Phew... feels good to have a well-organized library！
Rinko
It's not your duty day today, is it, ▲主人公＊▲...？
I couldn't leave some of the books out.
I can't believe you can't leave a book out, you're already a Library Committee member.
Eh, was I acknowledged as one just now...？
Yeah！
...It's a joke. Rinko will always rely on you the most. You know that, don't you？
(I'm kind of happy！)
Now I have a manuscript for the library newspaper！
Rinko
You worked especially hard this time, ▲主人公＊▲.
It was because of your continuous cooperation, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko only came up with the idea for the structure of the paper. You came up with all the content.
No, it's because you were doing the review section, ▲小早川＊▲...
We compliment each other, it's weird.
Haha, I know.
This is such a great effort, I hope everyone reads it.
Me too.
Well, let's use this momentum to plan the next issue, Mr. Editor-in-Chief.
(Editor-in-Chief... Okay, I'll do my best！)
Phew... I did a great job and finished organizing the bookshelves ahead of schedule！
Rinko
Good job. You did all this... by yourself, I see.
I've already learned the whole process without having to ask you ▲小早川＊▲.
I see. So you don't need Rinko anymore？ You'll be fine on your own.
Yeah, leave it to me！
Are you sure you want to be... alone？ If you're lonely without Rinko, why not just say you're lonely？
Yeah... I guess so. I still think we should do it together.
It can't be helped... If you say so, Rinko does not mind.
You know... I'll tell you what. Two Rinko's are better than one... hehe.
(Yeah, I agree！)
(I'm feeling kinda good today.)
Rinko
Hey！
What！！！？ You surprised me, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe. It was because you were spacing out.
I can't believe you...
Don't get angry, don't get angry. It's all fine.
...So, what's up？
Nothing much. I just... saw you swimming and decided to come visit...
It was kinda cool and you looked so strong...
Hehe... Rinko's boyfriend is... the kind of boyfriend you can brag about！
(I'm feeling embarrassed！)
Rinko
What's wrong, ▲小早川＊▲...？
Uh, yes... it's nothing.
Up close... you are surprisingly strong, or rather, your shoulders, your chest...
Huh？
Oh no, what am I saying？ Forget what I just said！ You must！
Y-Yes.
Come on, swim！ Hurry up！
(Alright, let's do it！)
